Module it.polimi.ingsw.PSP034

Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP034.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IRules
    Interface containing the methods that form the proper game rules.
    IStateManager
    Interface containing the methods used to arrange proper game actions (such as move, build, power, victory).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    Represents the board of the game.
    DefaultRules
    Contains default action rules used in the game.
    Game
    Contains the needed information on the state of the game.
    GodsRules
    Contains the god specific rules, decorating the main core: DefaultRules.
    Player
    Represents an active player in a given game.
    Tile
    Represents a single tile of the game board.
    Worker
    Represents a worker, associated to a player and on the game board.
